title: 11th Region volleyball pairings
text:
HERALD-LEADER Buy Photo 
The 11th Region volleyball tournament begins next Monday at Paul Laurence Dunbar. The winner advances to the state tournament, which tips off Friday, Nov. 6, at Valley in Louisville. 
Below are pairings for the 11th Region tournament. Dunbar advanced to the state tournament last season, snapping Henry Clay's streak of four straight 11th Region championships. 
Monday's first round 
Henry Clay (33-4) vs. Madison Southern (17-10), 6 p.m. Paul Dunbar (23-12) vs. Western Hills (23-13), 7:30 p.m. 
Tuesday's first round 
Madison Central (22-12) vs. Scott County (26-8), 6 p.m. Tates Creek (27-8) vs. Franklin County (6-22), 7:30 p.m.
